Ana sakin kwayoyin RNA na kwayar cutar a cikin cytoplasm; bayan kwayar cutar ta ninka, RNA na kwayar halitta tare da murfin glycoproteins da nucleopeptide sun hada da vesicles dauke da virion, wanda daga bisani ya haɗu da membrane plasma, yana haifar da sakin sabon kwayar cutar.
