A ranar 14 ga Fabrairun 2020, ƙungiyar Feng Zhang ta gabatar da yarjejeniya ta amfani da fasahar CRISPR-based SHERLOCK don gano SARS-CoV-2, wanda a ciki ake gano ɓangarorin RNA na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin girma daga <18->10 × 20 moles a kowace lita zuwa <18-</sup>10 × 200 moles a kowace lita (100-10 kwafi a kowane microliter na shigarwa) ta hanyar sanda a cikin ƙasa da awa ɗaya ba tare da buƙatar kayan aiki masu rikitarwa ba.
Ana fatan cewa sabon fasahar zai iya inganta ƙwarewa da kwanciyar hankali idan an tabbatar da shi a cikin gwajin asibiti.
Saboda rashin gogewa game da sabon coronavirus, likitoci galibi suna ba da kulawa ta tallafi ga marasa lafiyar COVID-19, yayin da suke ƙoƙarin amfani da matakan magani daban-daban waɗanda aka yi amfani da su ko aka ba da shawarar don magance ɓarkewar cutar coronavirus da ta gabata, gami da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV da sauran cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta (Table 2).
Wadannan magungunan sun hada da maganin psychoactive da yiwuwar maganin antiviral, masu hana rigakafi, steroids, plasma na marasa lafiya da suka warke, maganin kasar Sin da kuma goyon bayan tunani.
Har ma an ba da shawarar yin amfani da plasma na marasa lafiya da suka warke don magance sababbin marasa lafiya.
