Duk da haka, rashin lafiya da rashin ƙarfi na numfashi shine babban barazana ga marasa lafiya kuma shine babban dalilin mutuwa.
Don haka, hanyoyin taimakawa numfashi suna da mahimmanci don sauƙaƙe alamun cututtuka da ceton rayukan marasa lafiya kuma sun haɗa da maganin oxygen na yau da kullun, yawan zagayawar oxygen, iska mai ƙarancin iska da iska mai ƙarfi dangane da tsananin cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke fama da mummunan cututtukan numfashi dole ne a sanya su a ƙarƙashin ECMO, fasaha mai amfani da zuciya ta hanyar zuciya da aka yi amfani da ita don magance rashin ƙarfi na zuciya ko cututtukan numfashi.
Bugu da ƙari, kiyaye daidaiton electrolytes, rigakafi da maganin kamuwa da cuta na biyu da harin kamuwa da cuta da kare ayyukan gabobin jiki suna da mahimmanci ga marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
An tabbatar da cewa guguwar cytokine a cikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da SARS da MERS ta haifar da tsananin amsawar tsarin garkuwar jiki.
Cytokine cystine wani nau'i ne na halayen kumburi na tsarin da aka nuna ta hanyar sakin jerin cytokines ciki har da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ da MCP-1.
Wadannan cytokines suna motsa kwayoyin jikin mutum don sakin yawancin radicals kyauta wanda shine babban dalilin ARDS da rashin aiki na gabobin jiki.
Tsananta tsarin garkuwar jiki yana da mahimmanci a maganin guguwar cytokine, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
An yi amfani da corticosteroids da tuclizumab, wanda shine kwayar cutar monoclonal anti-IL6, don magance guguwar cytokine.
Sauran hanyoyin magance rigakafin rigakafin rigakafin cutar ta cytokine sun haɗa da: daidaitawar amsawar rigakafi ta hanyar T-cell; toshe aikin IFN-γ, IL-1 da TNF; hana JAK; Blenatumum; hana siginar cytokine 4; da masu hana HDAC.
Ana amfani da steroids a matsayin magungunan rigakafi don magance SARS don rage tsananin lalacewar kumburi.
Koyaya, steroids a cikin babban allurai ba su da amfani wajen warkar da mummunan lalacewar ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da SARS.
