An haɓaka dabarun allurar rigakafi ta amfani da ƙwayoyin cuta marasa aiki, plasmids na DNA, masu ɗaukar hoto, nanoparticles, ƙwayoyin cuta na kusan-kwayar cuta da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na MERS kuma an gwada su a kan wasu ƙirar dabbobi.
Samar da ingantaccen allurar rigakafi mai lafiya da inganci ga SARS-CoV-2 ga mutanen da ke da rauni a cikin rigakafi yana da gaggawa kuma yana da mahimmanci don sarrafa ci gaban cutar.
Koyaya, magance wannan matsala yana da ƙalubale saboda tsayin lokaci mai tsawo da ake buƙata don tsarawa da samar da allurar rigakafi (a matsakaita watanni 18) da canjin canjin coronavirus.
A matsayin sabon cuta, COVID-19 ya fara fara sake zagayowar asibiti a cikin dubban marasa lafiya.
A mafi yawan lokuta, marasa lafiya suna samun sauƙi a hankali kuma ba tare da wani ciwo ba.
Koyaya, kamar SARS da MERS, COVID-19 yana da alaƙa da rashin lafiya da mutuwa a cikin waɗanda ke fama da cutar mai tsanani.
Saboda haka, tsara samfurin gargadi na cutar yana da mahimmanci ga ƙungiyoyin kula da lafiya don ba da fifiko ga ayyukansu, musamman a yankunan da ke da iyakance albarkatu.
Dangane da nazarin asibiti da aka yi zuwa yanzu, abubuwan da ke ƙasa na iya tasiri ko alaƙa da ganewar asali na marasa lafiya na COVID-19 (Table 3):
Shekaru: Shekaru sune mafi mahimmancin abin da ke haifar da cutar SARS, kamar yadda yake tare da COVID-19.
COVID-19 galibi yana faruwa ne tsakanin shekaru 65-30, kamar yadda kashi 47.7 cikin ɗari na masu tsayi sama da shekaru 50 suka kamu da cutar a cikin binciken da aka yi da marasa lafiya 8,866 da aka bayyana a sama.
Marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman sun fi sha wahala daga cututtukan cututtuka da rikice-rikice na asali kuma sun fi tsufa fiye da marasa lafiya waɗanda ba sa buƙatar kulawa ta musamman (tare da matsakaicin shekaru 66 da 51), wanda ke ba da shawarar cewa ana iya ɗaukar shekaru a matsayin mai nuna alama ga sakamakon marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19.
Jima'i: Kamar yadda aka ambata a sama, SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da maza fiye da mata (0.31 cikin 100,000 idan aka kwatanta da 0.27 cikin 100,000).
Cutar cututtuka da rikice-rikice: Marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman suna iya samun rauni mai tsanani ko arrhythmias.
Cutar zuciya ita ce kuma babbar hanyar mutuwa a cikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar SARS.
An kuma bayar da rahoton cewa kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 na iya haɗuwa da kwayar cutar ta ACE2-positive, wanda zai iya haifar da lalacewar hanta a cikin marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Yana da mahimmanci a lura cewa shekaru da cututtukan cututtuka suna da dangantaka mai karfi kuma suna iya yin tasiri tare.
Binciken gwaje-gwaje na yau da kullun: Matsayin furotin mai amsawa na C a cikin jini yana nuna tsananin kumburi ko lalacewar nama kuma an ba da shawarar a matsayin mai yuwuwar gano cutar, amsawa ga magani da kuma murmurewa.
An ba da shawarar cewa akwai alaƙa tsakanin matakan CRP da tsananin cutar da cutar COVID-19.
Bugu da ƙari, ƙaruwa a cikin matakan lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT) da creatine kinase (CK) na iya taimakawa wajen hango sakamakon.
Wadannan enzymes suna bayyana a cikin yawancin kyallen takarda, musamman a zuciya da hanta, kuma ana sakin su yayin lalacewar kyallen takarda.
Saboda haka, suna da alamun gargajiya don gano cututtukan zuciya ko hanta.
Babban alamun asibiti: don hango abubuwan da ke faruwa da kuma rikice-rikice na COVID-19, radiography na kirji da ci gaban lokaci na alamun asibiti dole ne a yi la'akari da su tare da sauran batutuwan da suka shafi.
Amfani da steroids: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, steroids sune masu hana tsarin rigakafi wanda galibi ana amfani dasu azaman ƙarin magani don rage tsananin lalacewar kumburi a cikin yaƙi da cututtukan cututtuka.
Saboda ana amfani da allurai masu yawa na corticosteroids a cikin marasa lafiya masu fama da cutar SARS, yawancin waɗanda suka tsira daga cutar anemia sun sha wahala daga cutar ƙashin ƙashi tare da nakasa na dogon lokaci da ƙarancin rayuwa.
Don haka, idan ya zama dole, ya kamata a yi amfani da steroids a ƙananan allurai da gajeren lokaci ga marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Matsin lamba: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, yawancin marasa lafiya sun sami damuwa sosai yayin barkewar COVID-19 saboda yawanci ana tilasta su yin keɓewa na dogon lokaci, suna da shakku da shakku game da abin da ke faruwa, kuma suna ganin mutuwar danginsu ko abokai na kusa.
Bayar da shawarwari na ilimin halayyar dan adam da tallafi na dogon lokaci yana da mahimmanci don taimakawa waɗannan marasa lafiya su kawar da damuwa da komawa rayuwa ta al'ada.
Dangane da nazarin alƙaluma da aka yi zuwa yanzu, COVID-19 yana da halaye na annoba daban-daban idan aka kwatanta da SARS.
Kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 tana iya yin yawa a cikin ƙananan iska, kamar sauran COVID-19 na yau da kullun, a cikin ƙananan iska, yana nuna alamun rashin bayyanar cutar ko kuma ba tare da alamun cutar ba.
Saboda haka, marasa lafiya masu kamuwa da cutar a farkon lokaci ko lokacin da suka kamu da cutar za su iya samar da kwayar cutar da yawa a yayin ayyukan yau da kullun, wanda ke haifar da matsaloli da yawa don sarrafa cutar.
Koyaya, binciken ya nuna cewa SARS-CoV yana yaduwa yayin da marasa lafiya ke cikin mawuyacin hali, don haka yawancin lokuta ba sa yaduwa a farkon lokacin.
Don haka, cutar ta COVID-19 ta yanzu ta fi hatsari da wahala fiye da cutar SARS.
Ana yin ƙoƙari sosai a China, gami da cikakken sarrafawa da fita daga Wuhan da biranen da ke kewaye da shi da kuma keɓewar kusan dukkanin jama'a a cikin fatan dakatar da sarkar watsa SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da cewa waɗannan matakan sun yi mummunan lahani ga tattalin arziki da sauran sassan ƙasar, yawan sabbin masu cutar yana raguwa, wanda ke nuna cewa annobar ta ragu.
Hasashen mafi kyawun hasashe shine cewa barkewar cutar za ta ƙare a watan Maris, kuma za a ɗauki watanni 3 zuwa 4 don ci gaba da nazarin.
Duk da haka, wasu masana ba su da kyakkyawan fata.
Paul Hunter da abokan aikinsa sun kiyasta cewa annobar COVID-19, wacce ta fi cutar SARS saurin kamuwa da cuta, ba za ta ƙare a cikin 2020 ba.
Ira Langini da abokan aikinsa sun tsara samfurin don hango sakamakon annobar, suna ba da shawarar cewa SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da kashi biyu bisa uku na yawan mutanen duniya.
Wata ƙungiyar Kanada ta ba da rahoton cewa an gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin duka jerin samfuran swabs na hanci da makogwaro a cikin marasa lafiya da suka warke waɗanda aka sallama daga asibiti makonni biyu da suka gabata.
Koyaya, akwai kyakkyawan fata a China dangane da raguwar sabbin cututtukan da ke nuna yiwuwar nasarar dabarun yanzu.
Da farko an yi hasashen cewa cutar Ebola za ta kamu da mutane miliyan daya kuma ta kashe mutane miliyan biyar.
Duk da haka, ta hanyar keɓewa da keɓewa mai ƙarfi, cutar ta ƙarshe ta kasance ƙarƙashin iko.
Kamar SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mai rauni a hankali kuma daga ƙarshe ya ɓace ko ya canza zuwa kwayar cuta mai ƙarancin cututtuka wanda ke zaune tare da mutane.
Kwatanta cutar ta COVID-19 da SARS da MERS an nuna su a ƙasa (Figure 5).
SARS-CoV-2 yana da saurin yaduwa ta hanyar tari ko hancinsa kuma yana iya yaduwa ta hanyar hulɗa kai tsaye da abubuwan da ke dauke da kwayar cutar.
An kuma gano kwayar cutar a cikin kayan da ke cikin jijiyoyin jiki, wanda ke haifar da yiwuwar sabon kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar jijiyoyin jiki.
Wani binciken da aka yi kwanan nan akan marasa lafiya 138 ya ba da rahoton cewa kusan kashi 41 cikin ɗari na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar ta hanyar kamuwa da cuta ta asibiti, gami da marasa lafiya 17 da ke fama da wasu cututtuka da ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya 40.
Don haka, dole ne a yi taka tsantsan don kare mutane musamman ma ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya, ma'aikatan zamantakewa, dangin, abokan aiki har ma da waɗanda ke ziyartar marasa lafiya ko mutanen da ke da cutar.
Layin farko na kariya wanda za'a iya amfani dashi don rage haɗarin kamuwa da cutar shine sanya abin rufe fuska; amfani da masks na tiyata da masks na numfashi na N95 (jerin 1860s) suna taimakawa wajen sarrafa yaduwar ƙwayoyin cuta.
Masks na tiyata suna hana watsawa daga iska daga digo na ruwan numfashi daga kashin baya mai yuwuwar kamuwa da cutar zuwa wasu ko mannewa ga kayan abu sannan kuma bayan an watsa su zuwa wasu.
Koyaya, kawai masks na N95 (lambar jerin 1860s) na iya kare ku daga numfashin kwayoyin cutar da ke da girman 10 zuwa 80 nm, wanda kashi 5% na kwayoyin cutar ke iya shiga.
Saboda ana iya yin amfani da ƙananan abubuwa a tsakanin masks biyar na tiyata, masu ba da kiwon lafiya masu kula da lafiyar da ke hulɗa da marasa lafiya kai tsaye dole ne su yi amfani da masks na N95 (jerin 1860s) kuma su guji saka masks na tiyata.
Baya ga abin rufe fuska, ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya dole ne su sanya rigunan keɓewa waɗanda ke rufe su gaba ɗaya don rage haɗarin haɗuwa da cutar.
Kwayoyin cutar na iya kamuwa da mutum ta hanyar ido.
A ranar 22 ga Janairun 2020, wani likita ya kamu da SARS-CoV-2 yayin da yake sanye da abin rufe fuska na N95; mai yiwuwa ya shiga cikin jikinsa ta hanyar idanunsa masu kumburi.
Don haka, masu ba da sabis na kiwon lafiya masu kulawa dole ne su yi amfani da garkuwar fuska ko tabarau yayin kula da marasa lafiya.
Don kiyaye lafiyar jama'a a yankunan da ke dauke da cutar ko kuma masu yuwuwar kamuwa da cutar, ana ba da shawarar sosai cewa mutane su wanke hannayensu da sabulu mai kashe kwayoyin cuta fiye da yadda suka saba, su shiga keɓewa da zama a gida, da kuma iyakance hulɗa da mutanen da ke da yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar.
Matsakaicin da ya kamata tsakanin mutum da mai ciwo ya zama ƙafa uku.
Ana ganin waɗannan matakan sune ingantattun hanyoyi don ragewa da kuma hana yaduwar kwayar cutar.
Kodayake an san SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin sabon kwayar cutar ga ɗan adam, babban kamannin da yake da shi da SARS-CoV wanda aka ruwaito a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama babban gargaɗi ga China, yana tunatar da mu game da barkewar cutar SARS a 2003.
Koyaya, ba a yi ƙoƙari don tabbatar da kwanciyar hankali ba har zuwa 19 ga Janairun 2020, ranar da shugaban Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Wuhan ya ba da sanarwar cewa sabon kwayar cutar tana da ƙarancin kamuwa da cuta da iyakantaccen tasirin watsawa daga mutum zuwa mutum kuma ana iya hanawa da sarrafa cutar.
Wannan sakon ya sa ba a ɗauki gargadin jama'a da mahimmanci ba, musamman a lokacin da ƙasar ke shirin bikin Sabuwar Shekarar bazara, don haka an rasa babbar dama don hana yaduwar cutar a Wuhan.
Hukumomin kula da cututtuka a kasar Sin na iya koyon darasi daga wannan mummunan darasi kuma su yi wasu manyan ci gaba ga matakan da za a dauka nan gaba.
Misali, waɗannan ƙungiyoyin suna buƙatar (1) zama masu hankali yayin sanar da jama'a saboda duk wani abu da suka gabatar zai iya jan hankalin jama'a kuma ya canza ra'ayoyinsu da yanke shawara; (2) zama masu saurin amsawa ga bayanan da ba na al'ada ba daga wuraren asibiti, maimakon jiran rahotanni na hukuma daga likitoci ko hukumomin da ke da alhakin; (3) zama masu tsauraran matakai don hana yiwuwar barkewar cutar a farkon matakan maimakon kiran jama'a zuwa nutsuwa; (4) samar da ci gaba, ingantaccen bayani mai tasiri ga jama'a don haɓaka wayar da kan jama'a game da cutar ta annoba da kuma gwadawa da inganta tsarin amsawar al'umma a kai a kai.
Cutar COVID-19, wacce sabon kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa, ta fara a ƙarshen Disamba 2019.
A cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, cutar ta bazu ko'ina cikin China kuma a lokacin da ake rubuta wannan labarin, ta bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
Saboda kwayar cutar ta yi kama da SARS-CoV kuma alamun COVID-19 da SARS sun yi kama, barkewar COVID-19 ya haifar da tunanin cewa SARS ya dawo.
Koyaya, akwai wasu bambance-bambance da yawa tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS waɗanda ke da mahimmanci don hana yaduwar cutar da kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 yana shafar tsofaffi da maza fiye da matasa da mata, kuma yana da tsananin rauni da yawan mutuwa a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa.
Yawan mutuwar SARS ya fi na COVID-19 girma (10.91% vs. 1.44%).
Marasa lafiya da COVID-19 suna watsa cutar koda kuwa basu da alamomi, yayin da marasa lafiya na SARS galibi suna watsawa yayin da cutar ta yi tsanani, saboda haka hana yaduwar COVID-19 ya fi wahala idan aka kwatanta da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana wani ɓangare dalilin da yasa kwayar SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa da sauri kuma a kan sikelin da ya fi na SARS-CoV.
A wasu marasa lafiya na COVID-19, gwajin RNA na yau da kullun don gano SARS-CoV-2 na iya haifar da sakamako mara kyau.
A gefe guda kuma, marasa lafiya da suka warke za su iya sake kamuwa da cutar.
Wadannan binciken sun kara hadarin yaduwar kwayar cutar sosai.
Ganin irin wannan saurin ci gaban da aka samu a binciken COVID-19, har yanzu akwai wasu mahimman batutuwan da ba a warware su ba, gami da:
Daga ina ne kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta samo asali?
Kodayake an sami kashi 96% na jini tsakanin kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta bat, har yanzu ba za mu iya yanke shawarar cewa asalin SARS-CoV-2 daga bat ba.
Wane dabba ne ya kasance matsakaici don watsa kwayar cutar daga babban mai masaukin sa, jemage zuwa mutane?
Ba tare da sanin amsoshin tambayoyi 1 da 2 ba, ba za mu iya yanke sarkar watsawa yadda ya kamata ba, kuma ana iya sake barkewar cutar a kowane lokaci.
Kodayake ƙirar kwayoyin halitta da kimantawa na ilimin halittu sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 ya haɗu da mai karɓar ACE2, ta yaya ainihin kwayar cutar ta shiga cikin ƙwayoyin hanyar iska kuma ta haifar da sauye-sauyen cututtuka?
Shin kwayar cutar tana haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin bayyana ACE2 a wasu gabobin jiki?
