Bincike kan hulɗar COVID-19 a cikin dabbobi na iya ba mu mahimman bayanai game da cutar a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan binciken bita, muna ba da bayyani game da bayanan da ke akwai game da kwayar cutar HCoV guda bakwai da ke akwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da asalin dabbobi da kuma watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Mafi mahimmanci, muna kwatanta da kuma magance HCoVs daban-daban daga yanayin juyin halitta na kwayar cutar da kuma ba da izinin tsarin kwayoyin halitta.
Ana tattauna cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) a cikin wannan mahallin.
Bugu da ƙari, yanayin da ake buƙata don samun nasarar motsi tsakanin masu karɓar baƙi da kuma alamun ci gaban kwayar cutar a cikin yanayin cutar sun zama abin da aka fi mayar da hankali.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) suna cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na ƙwayoyin RNA masu ɗaure-ɗaure-da-ƙasa.
"Wadannan ƙwayoyin cuta, waɗanda ke da mafi girman kwayoyin halitta na 26-32 kilobes a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA, an kira su ""CoVs (coronavirus) "" ko ƙwayoyin cuta masu ɗauke da kambi saboda siffar su kamar kambi a ƙarƙashin microscope na lantarki. "
A matsayin tsari, coronaviruses suna da kwayoyin halittar guda daya wanda ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta sun hada da sassan karatu guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b) waɗanda ke fassara a matsayin polyprotein pp1a da pp1ab.
Ana sarrafa polyproteins don samar da sunadarai 16 marasa tsari waɗanda ake kira nsp1 zuwa 16.
Kwayar cuta ta genome ta ƙunshi ORFs don gina jiki, ciki har da spike (S), murfin kwayar cutar (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Yawancin ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman na asali suna ƙunshe da nau'ikan coronavirus daban-daban.
Dangane da bambancin tsari na furotin, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsuna huɗu (COV alpha, beta, gamma, da delta) kuma a cikinsu, jinsin beta na CoV ya ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an raba shi zuwa ƙananan layi huɗu (A, B, C, da D).
Shaidar phylogenetic ta nuna cewa jemage da rodents suna aiki a matsayin tushen kwayoyin halitta na yawancin alpha da beta coronaviruses, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban ma'ajiyar gamma da delta coronaviruses.
A cikin dubban shekaru, coronaviruses sun ci gaba da ƙetare shingen tsakanin jinsuna, wasu daga cikinsu sun zama manyan cututtukan mutum.
Zuwa yau, an gano nau'ikan HCoV guda bakwai.
Daga cikin su akwai HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63, waɗanda ke cikin alpha-CoVs.
Sauran nau'ikan beta guda biyar na COVID-19 sun haɗa da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da SARS-CoV-2.
