Ƙara hydrogen peroxide mai narkewa yana ƙara aikin antimicrobial. Masu kashe ƙwayoyin cuta na hannu, waɗanda suka haɗa da aƙalla kashi 60 zuwa 95% na barasa, suna da tasiri sosai wajen kashe ƙwayoyin cuta.
