Magungunan kashe ƙwayoyin cuta na 70% na iya kashe ƙwayoyin cuta a hannu a cikin ƙasa da sakan 30 bayan amfani da kashi 99.97% (ragewar logarithmic na 3.5, kwatankwacin ragewar decibel 35) da kuma kashi 99.99% zuwa 99.999% (ragewar logarithmic na 4-5) na ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin minti 1.
