Enzyme mai canzawa na Angiotensin-2B (ACE2 ) wani enzyme ne wanda ke haɗuwa da farfajiyar waje (ƙashin ƙwayoyin cuta) na ƙwayoyin huhu, jijiyoyin jini, zuciya, kuraje, da kuma amniotic.
ACE2 yana magance aikin enzyme mai canzawa ta hanyar rage yawan angiotensin 2 da haɓaka angiotensin 1-7, yana mai da shi makasudin magani mai tasiri don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 yana ci gaba da aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin don wasu coronaviruses.
Ana kiran nau'in enzyme na mutum da hACE2.
Enzyme mai canzawa na angiotensin-2 ya ƙunshi wani sinadarin zinc-ƙunshe da aka sanya a kan ƙwayoyin intravenous da sauran ƙwayoyin.
Furotin ACE2 ya ƙunshi yankin M2 peptidase N-terminal da yankin jigilar amino acid na polymerase C-terminal.
ACE2 shine nau'in furotin membrane mai nau'in guda ɗaya wanda ke da aikin aiki na enzyme wanda ke zaune a saman kwayoyin a cikin huhu da sauran kyallen takarda.
Wani enzyme mai suna Shadaz ya cire yankin waje na ACE2 daga cikin membrane, kuma furotin da aka samu ya sake shiga cikin jini kuma ya ƙare a cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin mafi yawan gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta na huhu, ƙananan ƙwayoyin hanji, ƙwayoyin intravascular da ƙwayoyin tsoka a cikin mafi yawan gabobin.
Ana kuma samun mRNA na ACE2 a cikin ƙwayar kwakwalwa, jikin jiki, hypothalamus da kuma kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine aiki azaman mai daidaita ACE.
ACE hormone ya raba angiotensin 1 zuwa angiotensin 2, wanda shine mai hana jini.
ACE2 a madadin haka, phenylalanine yana ware amino acid carboxyl-terminal daga angiotensin biyu (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana sarrafa shi zuwa angiotensin mai fadada jijiya (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya haifar da raguwa da yawa daga wasu peptides ciki har da /des-arg9-brededicin, neurotensin, dinorphine A da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita wucewar masu jigilar amino acid SLC6A19 daga membrane kuma yana da tasiri a cikin cututtukan zuciya.
ACE2 a matsayin furotin mai wucewa ta membrane, yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga kwayar halitta don wasu coronaviruses, gami da HCoV-NL63 (wanda ke haifar da SARS) da SARS-CoV-2 (wanda ke haifar da COVID-19).
